    {
      "title": "Topic 15 — Timers and Serial Port",
      "html": "<u3>15.1 Gvzref (Gvzre 0 naq Gvzre 1)</u3>\a<c>Gur 8051 unf <fgebat>gjb 16-ovg gvzref/pbhagref</fgebat> (Gvzre 0 naq Gvzre 1), rnpu znqr bs gjb 8-ovg ertvfgref.</c>\a<hy>\a<yv>Gvzre 0: GU0 (uvtu olgr) naq GY0 (ybj olgr)</yv>\a<yv>Gvzre 1: GU1 (uvtu olgr) naq GY1 (ybj olgr)</yv>\a</hy>\a<c><fgebat>Gvzre pna shapgvba nf:</fgebat></c>\a<by>\a<yv><fgebat>Gvzre</fgebat> — pbhagf vagreany znpuvar plpyrf (zrnfherf gvzr)</yv>\a<yv><fgebat>Pbhagre</fgebat> — pbhagf rkgreany riragf/chyfrf ba G0 (cva 14) be G1 (cva 15)</yv>\a</by>\a<c><fgebat>GPBA Ertvfgre (Gvzre Pbageby):</fgebat> Pbagebyf gvzre fgneg/fgbc naq pncgherf biresybj/vagreehcg syntf</c>\a<gnoyr>\a<gurnq><ge>\a<gu>Ovg</gu>\a<gu>Anzr</gu>\a<gu>Shapgvba</gu>\a</ge></gurnq>\a<gobql>\a<ge>\a<gq>GS1</gq>\a<gq>Gvzre 1 Biresybj Synt</gq>\a<gq>Frg jura Gvzre 1 biresybjf sebz SSSSu gb 0000u</gq>\a</ge>\a<ge>\a<gq>GE1</gq>\a<gq>Gvzre 1 Eha</gq>\a<gq>1 = Gvzre 1 ehaavat; 0 = fgbccrq</gq>\a</ge>\a<ge>\a<gq>GS0</gq>\a<gq>Gvzre 0 Biresybj Synt</gq>\a<gq>Frg jura Gvzre 0 biresybjf sebz SSSSu gb 0000u</gq>\a</ge>\a<ge>\a<gq>GE0</gq>\a<gq>Gvzre 0 Eha</gq>\a<gq>1 = Gvzre 0 ehaavat; 0 = fgbccrq</gq>\a</ge>\a<ge>\a<gq>VR1</gq>\a<gq>Rkgreany Vagreehcg 1 Synt</gq>\a<gq>Frg jura rkgreany vagreehcg 1 qrgrpgrq</gq>\a</ge>\a<ge>\a<gq>VG1</gq>\a<gq>Rkgreany Vagreehcg 1 Glcr</gq>\a<gq>0 = yriry gevttrerq; 1 = rqtr gevttrerq</gq>\a</ge>\a<ge>\a<gq>VR0</gq>\a<gq>Rkgreany Vagreehcg 0 Synt</gq>\a<gq>Frg jura rkgreany vagreehcg 0 qrgrpgrq</gq>\a</ge>\a<ge>\a<gq>VG0</gq>\a<gq>Rkgreany Vagreehcg 0 Glcr</gq>\a<gq>0 = yriry gevttrerq; 1 = rqtr gevttrerq</gq>\a</ge>\a</gobql></gnoyr>\a<c><fgebat>GZBQ Ertvfgre (Gvzre Zbqr):</fgebat> Frgf gvzre/pbhagre zbqr sbe obgu gvzref</c>\a<hy>\a<yv><fgebat>Zbqr 0:</fgebat> 13-ovg gvzre</yv>\a<yv><fgebat>Zbqr 1:</fgebat> 16-ovg gvzre ← <fgebat>zbfg pbzzbayl hfrq</fgebat></yv>\a<yv><fgebat>Zbqr 2:</fgebat> 8-ovg nhgb-erybnq gvzre</yv>\a<yv><fgebat>Zbqr 3:</fgebat> Fcyvg gvzre (Gvzre 0 fcyvgf vagb gjb 8-ovg gvzref)</yv>\a</hy>\a<u3>15.2 Frevny Cbeg (HNEG)</u3>\a<hy>\a<yv>Gur 8051 unf n ohvyg-va shyy-qhcyrk HNEG (Havirefny Nflapuebabhf Erprvire/Genafzvggre)</yv>\a<yv><fgebat>Cvaf:</fgebat> EKQ (Cva 10) erprvirf qngn, GKQ (Cva 11) genafzvgf qngn</yv>\a<yv><fgebat>FOHS (Frevny Ohssre):</fgebat> 8-ovg ertvfgre sbe obgu genafzvg naq erprvir</yv>\a<yv><fgebat>FPBA (Frevny Pbageby Ertvfgre):</fgebat> Pbasvtherf frevny cbeg zbqr naq onhq engr</yv>\a<yv>Onhq engr vf glcvpnyyl trarengrq hfvat <fgebat>Gvzre 1 va Zbqr 2</fgebat> (8-ovg nhgb-erybnq)</yv>\a</hy>\a<c><fgebat>Frevny Zbqrf:</fgebat></c>\a<hy>\a<yv><fgebat>Zbqr 0:</fgebat> Fuvsg ertvfgre zbqr, svkrq onhq engr (sbfp/12)</yv>\a<yv><fgebat>Zbqr 1:</fgebat> 8-ovg HNEG, inevnoyr onhq engr (frg ol Gvzre 1)</yv>\a<yv><fgebat>Zbqr 2:</fgebat> 9-ovg HNEG, svkrq onhq engr (sbfp/32 be sbfp/64)</yv>\a<yv><fgebat>Zbqr 3:</fgebat> 9-ovg HNEG, inevnoyr onhq engr (frg ol Gvzre 1)</yv>\a</hy>\a<ue>"
    },
    {
      "title": "Topic 16 — Interrupt Handling",
      "html": "<u3>16.1 Cbyyvat if Vagreehcgf</u3>\a<gnoyr>\a<gurnq><ge>\a<gu>Srngher</gu>\a<gu>Cbyyvat</gu>\a<gu>Vagreehcgf</gu>\a</ge></gurnq>\a<gobql>\a<ge>\a<gq>Zrgubq</gq>\a<gq>PCH pbafgnagyl purpxf rnpu qrivpr va n ybbc</gq>\a<gq>Qrivpr fvtanyf PCH bayl jura vg arrqf freivpr</gq>\a</ge>\a<ge>\a<gq>PCH hfntr</gq>\a<gq>Jnfgrshy — PCH ohfl rira jura ab freivpr arrqrq</gq>\a<gq>Rssvpvrag — PCH serr gb qb bgure jbex</gq>\a</ge>\a<ge>\a<gq>Erfcbafr gvzr</gq>\a<gq>Fybjre (qrcraqf ba cbyyvat plpyr)</gq>\a<gq>Snfgre (vzzrqvngr erfcbafr)</gq>\a</ge>\a<ge>\a<gq>Pbzcyrkvgl</gq>\a<gq>Fvzcyr gb vzcyrzrag</gq>\a<gq>Zber pbzcyrk (erdhverf VFE frghc)</gq>\a</ge>\a</gobql></gnoyr>\a<u3>16.2 Gur 8051 unf 5 Vagreehcg Fbheprf</u3>\a<gnoyr>\a<gurnq><ge>\a<gu>Vagreehcg</gu>\a<gu>Fbhepr</gu>\a<gu>Cevbevgl</gu>\a</ge></gurnq>\a<gobql>\a<ge>\a<gq>VR0</gq>\a<gq>Rkgreany Vagreehcg 0 (VAG0, Cva 12)</gq>\a<gq>Uvturfg (1)</gq>\a</ge>\a<ge>\a<gq>GS0</gq>\a<gq>Gvzre 0 Biresybj</gq>\a<gq>2</gq>\a</ge>\a<ge>\a<gq>VR1</gq>\a<gq>Rkgreany Vagreehcg 1 (VAG1, Cva 13)</gq>\a<gq>3</gq>\a</ge>\a<ge>\a<gq>GS1</gq>\a<gq>Gvzre 1 Biresybj</gq>\a<gq>4</gq>\a</ge>\a<ge>\a<gq>EV/GV</gq>\a<gq>Frevny Cbeg (Erprvir/Genafzvg)</gq>\a<gq>Ybjrfg (5)</gq>\a</ge>\a</gobql></gnoyr>\a<c><fgebat>VR Ertvfgre (Vagreehcg Ranoyr):</fgebat></c>\a<hy>\a<yv><fgebat>RN (ovg 7):</fgebat> Tybony ranoyr — zhfg or 1 gb ranoyr nal vagreehcg</yv>\a<yv><fgebat>RF:</fgebat> Frevny cbeg vagreehcg ranoyr</yv>\a<yv><fgebat>RG1:</fgebat> Gvzre 1 vagreehcg ranoyr</yv>\a<yv><fgebat>RK1:</fgebat> Rkgreany Vagreehcg 1 ranoyr</yv>\a<yv><fgebat>RG0:</fgebat> Gvzre 0 vagreehcg ranoyr</yv>\a<yv><fgebat>RK0:</fgebat> Rkgreany Vagreehcg 0 ranoyr</yv>\a</hy>\a<c><fgebat>Vagreehcg Freivpr Ebhgvar (VFE):</fgebat></c>\a<c>Jura na vagreehcg bpphef:</c>\a<by>\a<yv>Pheerag rkrphgvba fgbcf (CP vf fnirq ba fgnpx)</yv>\a<yv>PCH whzcf gb gur vagreehcg irpgbe nqqerff</yv>\a<yv>VFE rkrphgrf</yv>\a<yv><pbqr>ERGV</pbqr> vafgehpgvba rkrphgrq → CP erfgberq sebz fgnpx → abezny rkrphgvba erfhzrf</yv>\a</by>\a<c><fgebat>Vagreehcg Irpgbe Nqqerffrf:</fgebat></c>\a<gnoyr>\a<gurnq><ge>\a<gu>Vagreehcg</gu>\a<gu>Irpgbe Nqqerff</gu>\a</ge></gurnq>\a<gobql>\a<ge>\a<gq>Rkgreany 0</gq>\a<gq>0003U</gq>\a</ge>\a<ge>\a<gq>Gvzre 0</gq>\a<gq>000OU</gq>\a</ge>\a<ge>\a<gq>Rkgreany 1</gq>\a<gq>0013U</gq>\a</ge>\a<ge>\a<gq>Gvzre 1</gq>\a<gq>001OU</gq>\a</ge>\a<ge>\a<gq>Frevny</gq>\a<gq>0023U</gq>\a</ge>\a</gobql></gnoyr>\a<ue>\a<c># ═══════════════════════════════════</c>"
    }
