      "title": "Topic 3.8 — Guided Media: UTP, STP, Coaxial & Optical Fiber",
      "html": "<u3>📖 Pber Gurbel</u3>\a<c>Thvqrq zrqvn qverpgf ryrpgebzntargvp jnirf nybat n fbyvq culfvpny cngu.</c>\a<hy>\a<yv><fgebat>HGC (Hafuvryqrq Gjvfgrq Cnve)</fgebat>: Pbafvfgf bs pbybe-pbqrq pbccre jverf gjvfgrq va cnvef gb erqhpr pebffgnyx naq RZV. Uvtuyl syrkvoyr naq pbfg-rssrpgvir, ohg fhfprcgvoyr gb abvfr. Hfrf <fgebat>EW-45</fgebat> pbaarpgbef. Fgnaqneqvmrq ol pngrtbevrf (r.t. Png5r fhccbegf 1 Tocf, Png6 fhccbegf 10 Tocf hc gb 55z, Png6n fhccbegf 10 Tocf hc gb 100z).</yv>\a<yv><fgebat>FGC (Fuvryqrq Gjvfgrq Cnve)</fgebat>: Nqqf n zrgny sbvy fuvryq nebhaq jver cnvef gb zvavzvmr RZV. Zber rkcrafvir naq evtvq guna HGC; erdhverf tebhaqvat.</yv>\a<yv><fgebat>Pbnkvny Pnoyr</fgebat>: Bhgre cynfgvp wnpxrg → pbccre oenvq fuvryq → qvryrpgevp vafhyngbe → fbyvq pbccre pber. Hfrq sbe pnoyr GI naq uvtu-serdhrapl nccyvpngvbaf. Zbqrf:</yv>\a<yv><rz>Onfronaq</rz>: Fvatyr punaary, pneevrf qvtvgny fvtanyf.</yv>\a<yv><rz>Oebnqonaq</rz>: Zhygvcyr punaaryf, pneevrf nanybt fvtanyf.</yv>\a<yv><fgebat>Bcgvpny Svore</fgebat>: Genafzvgf qngn nf yvtug chyfrf guebhtu n uvtu-chevgl tynff pber. Hfrf <fgebat>Gbgny Vagreany Ersyrpgvba</fgebat>: gur tynff pber vf jenccrq va n <fgebat>pynqqvat</fgebat> jvgu n ybjre ersenpgvir vaqrk, ersyrpgvat yvtug onpx vagb gur pber. Glcrf:</yv>\a<yv><rz>Fvatyr-Zbqr</rz>: Aneebj pber, ynfre fbhepr. Zvavzvmrf qvfcrefvba, vqrny sbe ybat qvfgnaprf.</yv>\a<yv><rz>Zhygv-Zbqr</rz>: Jvqr pber, YRQ fbhepr. Yvtug ersyrpgvbaf geniry zhygvcyr cnguf, pnhfvat zbqny qvfcrefvba. Orfg sbe fubeg pnzchf qvfgnaprf.</yv>\a</hy>\a<u3>📝 cenpgvpr ZPDf</u3>\a<qvi pynff=\"zpd-pneq\">\a  <qvi pynff=\"zpd-dhrfgvba\"><fgebat>D1.</fgebat> Jung culfvpny curabzraba nyybjf yvtug gb geniry guebhtu gur tynff pber bs n svore-bcgvp pnoyr jvgubhg rfpncvat?</qvi>\a  <qvi pynff=\"zpd-bcgvbaf\" qngn-pbeerpg=\"o\">\a    <qvi pynff=\"zpd-bcgvba\" qngn-bcgvba=\"n\">\a      <fcna pynff=\"bcgvba-yrggre\">n)</fcna>\a      <fcna pynff=\"bcgvba-grkg\">Ersenpgvba</fcna>\a    </qvi>\a    <qvi pynff=\"zpd-bcgvba\" qngn-bcgvba=\"o\">\a      <fcna pynff=\"bcgvba-yrggre\">o)</fcna>\a      <fcna pynff=\"bcgvba-grkg\">Gbgny Vagreany Ersyrpgvba</fcna>\a    </qvi>\a    <qvi pynff=\"zpd-bcgvba\" qngn-bcgvba=\"p\">\a      <fcna pynff=\"bcgvba-yrggre\">p)</fcna>\a      <fcna pynff=\"bcgvba-grkg\">Bcgvpny Qvfcrefvba</fcna>\a    </qvi>\a    <qvi pynff=\"zpd-bcgvba\" qngn-bcgvba=\"q\">\a      <fcna pynff=\"bcgvba-yrggre\">q)</fcna>\a      <fcna pynff=\"bcgvba-grkg\">Fvtany Nggrahngvba</fcna>\a    </qvi>\a  </qvi>\a</qvi>\a<qvi pynff=\"zpd-pneq\">\a  <qvi pynff=\"zpd-dhrfgvba\"><fgebat>D2.</fgebat> Haqre GVN fgnaqneqf, juvpu gjvfgrq-cnve pngrtbel vf qrfvtarq gb fhccbeg 10 Tocf qngn engrf hc gb 100 zrgref?</qvi>\a  <qvi pynff=\"zpd-bcgvbaf\" qngn-pbeerpg=\"p\">\a    <qvi pynff=\"zpd-bcgvba\" qngn-bcgvba=\"n\">\a      <fcna pynff=\"bcgvba-yrggre\">n)</fcna>\a      <fcna pynff=\"bcgvba-grkg\">Png5r</fcna>\a    </qvi>\a    <qvi pynff=\"zpd-bcgvba\" qngn-bcgvba=\"o\">\a      <fcna pynff=\"bcgvba-yrggre\">o)</fcna>\a      <fcna pynff=\"bcgvba-grkg\">Png6</fcna>\a    </qvi>\a    <qvi pynff=\"zpd-bcgvba\" qngn-bcgvba=\"p\">\a      <fcna pynff=\"bcgvba-yrggre\">p)</fcna>\a      <fcna pynff=\"bcgvba-grkg\">Png6n</fcna>\a    </qvi>\a    <qvi pynff=\"zpd-bcgvba\" qngn-bcgvba=\"q\">\a      <fcna pynff=\"bcgvba-yrggre\">q)</fcna>\a      <fcna pynff=\"bcgvba-grkg\">Png3</fcna>\a    </qvi>\a  </qvi>\a</qvi>\a<ue>"
